74
00:05:13,700 --> 00:05:17,100
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">In Loguetown... in the East Blue!</font>

75
00:05:17,100 --> 00:05:21,920
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">On the legendary execution stand,
where the Pirate King Roger himself died!</font>

76
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:25,120
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Trapped in a hopeless position, that man declared...</font>

77
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:29,240
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>I'm the man who will be the Pirate King!</i></font>

78
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:35,300
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">And in that moment, the heavens...</font>

