00:05:38,220 --> 00:05:42,970
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">brought down the lightning, and saved him!</font>

80
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:47,190
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I witnessed a miracle!</font>

81
00:05:50,980 --> 00:05:55,940
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Ever since that day, I fanatically read
everything I could about the Straw Hat Pirates.</font>

82
00:05:55,940 --> 00:06:00,790
